title: All 12 Books In The Barsoom Series In Plain Text And Java Format
description:
All 12 books in the Barsoom Series by Edgar Rice Burroughs in both plain text and .JAR formats for JAVA phones,

1     Princess Of Mars
2     The Gods Of Mars 
3     Warlord Of Mars
4     Thuvia, Maid Of Mars
5     The Chessmen Of Mars
6     The Mastermind Of Mars
7     A Fighting Man Of Mars
8     Swords Of Mars
9     Synthetic Men Of Mars
10    LLana Of Gathol
11    John Carter And The Giant Of Mars
12    Skeleton Men Of Mars
